'''IP基于HTTPS'''（{{lang|en|'''IP over HTTPS'''}}，或'''IP-HTTPS'''、'''MS-IPHTTPS'''）是一个[[微软|微软]]的[[隧道协议|隧道协议]]。IP-HTTPS协议与早期的[[6to4|6to4]]和[[Teredo隧道|Teredo隧道]]机制类似，它使[[IPv6|IPv6]]数据包可以在非IPv6网络上传输。

== 微软对过渡协议的偏好 ==
微软过去常常不鼓励使用IP-HTTPS，因为它的速度较慢<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/tomshinder/2010/03/30/more-on-directaccess-split-tunneling-and-force-tunneling/|title=More on DirectAccess Split Tunneling and Force Tunneling|author=Tom Shinder|date=2010-03-30|publisher=Microsoft|quote=The problem with IP-HTTPS is that it should be considered, and is instantiated as, a protocol of last resort. [...] the primary reason being that it’s the lowest performing of the IPv6 transition technology protocols.|accessdate=2016-12-17|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823073942/https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/tomshinder/2010/03/30/more-on-directaccess-split-tunneling-and-force-tunneling/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

对于[[Windows_Server_2012|Windows Server 2012]]，微软改变了该协议的内部工作原理，IP-HTTPS现在是其[[DirectAccess|DirectAccess]] VPN技术的“首选IPv6过渡技术”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/tip_of_the_day/2013/11/11/tip-of-the-day-direct-access-and-ip-https/|title=Tip of the Day: Direct Access and IP-HTTPS|author=Robert Mitchell|date=2013-11-11|publisher=Microsoft|quote=IP-HTTPS is now the preferred IPv6 transition technology for DirectAccess.|accessdate=2016-12-17|archive-date=2019-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216161621/https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/tip_of_the_day/2013/11/11/tip-of-the-day-direct-access-and-ip-https/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

